</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">VTuber艺人配发也已开始</h3><p>这部作品也开始被VTuber达人纷纷直播。</p><p>一月中旬，Hololive Productions 人员将开始提前发行游戏。截至 1 月 21 日，Buspo！ 、Neo-Porte、Nanashi Inku的附属艺人以及个人艺人也开始流出。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【伙伴世界】和三山文美子一起来到残酷的世界吧！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ ！ [hololive/佐仓巫女]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j20R83J_U2c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[Palworld] 看起来很有趣 Fullpa（？） [Buispo！ /英文丽莎]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TGgnLpw9wYU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[PALWORLD]想尝试一下备受关注的PAL WORLD吗？[涩谷Haru]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G-KdDGAjo3U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[PALWORLD] 我用一款热门游戏进行了一次大冒险！ [木崎红子 / Nanashinku]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ksI_T5-sIno?feature=oembed" frameb